Henry W. Pardo et al. v. John Bittorf. Submitted October 4, 1881. Aikmson dk Aildnson against.

Motion to dismiss — Settlement of case.

Where a case is not heard on testimony taken in open court there is-nothing to settle, and a motion to dismiss such a case on the ground, that it has not been settled will be denied.

Motion to dismiss.

Denied October 5.

Fraser dk Gates for the motion.
